==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Limestone
<hw>Lime"stone`</hw> <pr>(l⟦imac⟧m"st⟦omac⟧n`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<def>A rock consisting chiefly of calcium carbonate or carbonate of
lime. It sometimes contains also magnesium carbonate, and is then called
<xex>magnesian</xex> or <xex>dolomitic limestone</xex>. Crystalline
limestone is called <xex>marble</xex>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lime twig</ent>⟦br⟧
